# DTD Parser

[![Build Status](https://github.com/eclipse-ee4j/jaxb-dtd-parser/actions/workflows/maven.yml/badge.svg?branch=master)](https://github.com/eclipse-ee4j/jaxb-dtd-parser/actions/workflows/maven.yml?branch=master)
